{"tid":808350,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"剛剛我正大光明咁係老母面前倒左碗湯","createTime":"2018-09-06T09:13:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-07T04:05:10.000Z","uid":1734,"like":65,"dislike":706,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"91ae8b5c6d091d51e5589c41cae181450fcd46fb","tid":808350,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T09:13:33.000Z","msg":"話說頭先我打緊lol個陣<br />\n我老母無端端捧碗湯入黎叫我飲左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁打緊Lol又點分神飲湯 咁咪話一陣飲<br />\n點知我老母5分鐘入黎煩我一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後我頂唔撚順係佢面前倒晒佢碗湯落地下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住佢眼濕濕扮委屈咁拖返乾撻地 我心諗你一開始唔好咁煩咪得囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你逼我飲我就係都唔飲呀你吹咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"130f90be5d0a1b782b7f53deb94842ab4bf24a0a","tid":808350,"uid":70195,"like":66,"dislike":2,"score":64,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T09:14:44.000Z","msg":"樓主好撚25"},{"pid":"70c480f5f78561aa9a22db448402ce37563ac917","tid":808350,"uid":194966,"like":12,"dislike":17,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T09:15:33.000Z","msg":"2/10 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcd5028394653e8f604f384f9575c8fb0bb6f469","tid":808350,"uid":1734,"like":2,"dislike":20,"score":-18,"quote":{"pid":"130f90be5d0a1b782b7f53deb94842ab4bf24a0a","tid":808350,"uid":70195,"like":66,"dislike":2,"score":64,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T09:14:44.000Z","msg":"樓主好撚25"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T09:16:02.000Z","msg":"鬼叫佢煩住曬 話左唔飲住"},{"pid":"4408f6749448609a90a927f02e68cfa6fc655753","tid":808350,"uid":159448,"like":191,"dislike":0,"score":191,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T09:16:10.000Z","msg":"要回幾次帶？"},{"pid":"781e253eb6f0a82691de6d3645770964f36633b7","tid":808350,"uid":134231,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"c